Otherwise, even if the renovation is done,

145
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:47,070
I'm afraid no one will buy it.

146
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:49,230
I think at this point,

147
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:52,630
