151
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:00,670
Then

152
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:04,190
I actually have another idea.

153
00:08:07,030 --> 00:08:08,950
I think you can stop your work.

154
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:11,230
